cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Polygraph, please cite the paper that introduces the method."
title: "Polygraph — a polygraph for your state machine"
abstract: >-
  A Claude Code plugin for trace-driven consistency checking of stateful code:
  derive a bare next(state, action, data) transition function from a program's
  own source with an LLM, replay real execution traces against it, and surface
  every disagreement as a spec-error, code-finding, or contract-error.
authors:
